S. L. Jung, M. Y. Chang, J. Y. 
      Jyang, L. C. Yeh, and Y. Y. Tzou, “Design and implementation of an FPGA-based 
      control IC for AC-voltage regulation,” IEEE Trans. on Power Electron., 
      vol. 14, no. 3, pp. 522-532, May. 1999.

A. Prodic, D. Maksimovic, and R. 
      Erickson, “Design and implementation of a digital PWM controller for a 
      high-frequency switching DC-DC power converter,” IEEE IECON Conf. Rec., 
      2001.

B. J. Patella, A. Prodic, A. 
      Zirger, and D. Maksimovic, “High-frequency digital controller IC for dc/dc 
      converters,” IEEE APEC Conf. Rec., pp. 374–380, 2002. 

